
1. Install:
go get -u github.com/go-redis/redis

2. Build golang:
env GOOS=linux GOARCH=amd64 go build -v -ldflags "-X main.version=v1.0.0" -o build

3. docker build image and run
docker build --force-rm . -t goweb:1.0   
docker run -itd --network=small --name gogo -p 55555:55555 goweb:1.0

note: 
* generate m3u8 with ffmpeg
ffmpeg -i sample.mp4 -c:v libx264 -c:a aac -strict -2 -hls_list_size 0 -hls_time 20 -f hls output.m3u8
* demo.tar.gz could be found on nginx_php
* localdemo.tar.gz is similar with demo.tar.
* encdemo.tar.gz use the encryption with hls

4. Nginx note: https://www.nginx.com/resources/wiki/start/topics/tutorials/config_pitfalls/